  "instructions": [
    "Combine yeast, warm water, and 1 tsp sugar in a bowl; let sit for 5 minutes.",
    "Add olive oil, onion, garlic, bonito flakes, cumin, coriander, salt, and pepper to the yeast mixture; mix well.",
    "Add frozen seafood mix to the claypot; pour in yeast mixture and mix gently.",
    "Cover claypot and let it sit in a warm place for 30 minutes.",
    "Preheat oven to 375\u001238f (190\u001323c).",
    "Place claypot in the oven and roast for 20-25 minutes or until the seafood is cooked through.",
    "Remove claypot from the oven and stir in lemon juice and chopped parsley.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
